Condition : 11 - A Car Park Management Plan shall be submitted and approved in writing by the Local Planning Authority prior to superstructure works commencing. The Plan shall include the following:

"	details and location of 20% electric vehicle charging points and details of a further 20% passive provision;
"	details of parking layout; 
"	details of parking space allocation policy and management regime ensuring the disabled spaces be used by 'Blue Badge' holders 

The details shall be carried out before first occupation of any part of the development and maintained as such thereafter.
